OL,3,CPolitical newcomer elected to
OL,4,CGuernsey's top civic committee
OL,6,FDeputy Andrew Niles has been elected
OL,7,Fto Guernsey's top political committee
OL,8,Fby States Members.
OL,10,FDeputy Niles, who is a relative
OL,11,Fnewcomer to the States, told ITV News
OL,12,Fthat he joins the Committee for Policy
OL,13,Fand Resources (P&R) at a challenging
OL,14,Ftime.
OL,16,FIt follows the resignation of former
OL,17,FChief Minister Deputy Gavin St Pier,
OL,18,Fwho stepped down earlier this month
OL,19,Fafter he was arrested on suspicion of
OL,20,Fmisconduct in public office.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
