OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1779369077
OL,3,CPolitical newcomer elected to
OL,4,CGuernsey's top civic committee
OL,6,FHe denies the allegations, and no
OL,7,Fcharges have been brought against him.
OL,9,FDeputy St Pier put himself forward as
OL,10,Fa candidate for re-election - as well
OL,11,Fas Deputy Haley Camp - but both were
OL,12,Fdefeated in the States today
OL,13,F(Wednesday 20 May).
OL,15,FDeputy Niles told ITV News: "I think
OL,16,Fthat the States is about to undergo
OL,17,Fsome pretty rigorous tests to go
OL,18,Fthrough its fiscal plan that it needs
OL,19,Fto deliver in the summer.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1779369077
OL,3,CPolitical newcomer elected to
OL,4,CGuernsey's top civic committee
OL,6,F"I think that it needs to have some
OL,7,Fcool heads. It needs to have some
OL,8,Funderstanding of where we're going,
OL,9,Fand I think that I can help deliver
OL,10,Fthat."
OL,12,FOne of Deputy Niles' supporters,
OL,13,FDeputy Steve Falla, who already sits
OL,14,Fon P&R, says his commercial
OL,15,Fconnections will be a key asset for
OL,16,Fthe Committee.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1779369077
OL,3,CPolitical newcomer elected to
OL,4,CGuernsey's top civic committee
OL,6,F"Whilst he's new to the States
OL,7,FAssembly, this term, he was a non-
OL,8,Fvoting member on the Economic
OL,9,FDevelopment Committee last term,"
OL,10,FDeputy Falla explained.
OL,12,F"I sat with him on that Committee, and
OL,13,FI think he won't, in that sense, be
OL,14,Fhitting the ground running on P&R, but
OL,15,Fhe knows his way around, and he comes
OL,16,Ffrom a very longstanding business
OL,17,Fcareer which positions him very well
OL,18,Ffor lots of the things we're facing at
OL,19,Fthe moment."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
