PN,38205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1779369077
OL,3,CPolitical newcomer elected to
OL,4,CGuernsey's top civic committee
OL,6,FDeputy St Pier told ITV News that his
OL,7,Ffailed re-election bid was
OL,8,F"unfortunate", adding that the
OL,9,Felection was something no States
OL,10,FMembers wanted.
OL,12,F"It was as a result of circumstances
OL,13,Fin which information was put in the
OL,14,Fpublic domain, that wouldn't otherwise
OL,15,Fbe here, that's forced the situation
OL,16,Fto arise," Deputy St Pier said.
OL,18,F"It's unfortunate, but this is where
OL,19,Fwe are."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/6
